REMARK_EN: THE "E" FOR DISCHARGES BELOW 1.040 M3/S IS DUE TO LOW WATER CURVE EXTENSION.
REMARK_FR: LE < E > POUR LES DEBITS INFERIEURS A 1,040 M3/S EN RAISON DU PROLONGEMENT DE LA COURBE D'ETIAGE.

REMARK_EN: THE "E" FOR DISCHARGES ON SEP 10-11 IS DUE TO CURVE EXTENSION.
REMARK_FR: LE < E > POUR LES DEBITS DES 10 ET 11 SEP INDIQUE UN PROLONGEMENT DE LA COURBE.

REMARK_EN:
MISSING WATER LEVELS BETWEEN JUL 9 and SEP 10 IS DUE TO INSTRUMENT MALFUNCTION.
THE 'E' FOR DISCHARGES BETWEEN JAN 8 & SEP 11 IS DUE TO INSTRUMENT MALFUNCTION.
